post.body: YES WE CAN!
Voted! YES WE CAN!
In line to get my ballot! Have been at my poll since 5:45. Am soooooo excited! YES WE CAN!
So these are my neighbors? I don't recognize anybody. But god bless 'em!
So many dyke couples at eastern regionals it could be a Lilith Fair!
Bay area's intro presentation to the jefferson's theme song (movin on up!) is so excellent that for a moment I stop hating them!
The big lesson of yesterday: don't wear flip-flops to roller derby events!
Bothering JFM in the derby news network booth.
Watching KCRdub play Denver. Up 56-32 25 mins in. I'm benched and sad about it although I'm psyched Eclipse gets to play today.
Rose city has 5 or 6 support staff on shoes at their bench and BAD has 3. You're allowed 2. It doesn't seem to be difference for portland
Bruz talking about a BAD girl's tits hanging out: in gymnastics they keep that shi locked up! In swimming, they keep that shit locked up!
Bruz sez: don't coach! ...why should they listen to us anyway?! Ha ha ha ha ha ha!
At bay area vs rose city. Fast skating, how refreshing! I yell "slow down, stop stop!" the bay area pack hears me and does; it works!
Coach ice congratulated me for having a good game last night and he doesn't generally dole out complements! Same with Bruz, said I was great
I woke up at 5am. Want to meet bruz for coffee asap
Oops, we lost our qualifier.
Suiting up! Rah rah!
In the van, headed to the venue. Ready to K.I.L.L. Doobie Doobie Doo!
Law&order was on. I said I felt ready to kill Duke City. Dominant Jean said she was ready to kill, investigate, and take Duke City to court.
Team meeting at 3:30. Then to bout venue, we warm up during halftime of the prior game, then 15 mins btw games. Gametime 6:15.
